text: Kothiala is one of the 51 Union Councils of Abbottabad District in the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa province of Pakistan. ==Subdivisions== Bagakot - Naka - Nalla - Doga - jab - Gali Syedan - Golra - Panyali - Salyot - Sora - Mukdabi Gup - Brahan - Todumira - Nalla (tudumira) - Tali - Misser -karmatti- Poona - Chakuli - Cheera thandi Khuiy - Hall Syedian - Tarada - Mubarak - Kalya - Char - Lunda - Daki -Beeri Patyan - Cahri - Banjgalli - Paswal - Soban Galli - Chariala - ==Tribes== The main tribes are: Tanolis Awan Syed Gujr ==References== Category:Union councils of Abbottabad District
